Cloud Security ( Important for the Industry POV)

Identity & Access Management (IAM)
MFA (Multi-factor authentication)
Encryption (At-rest + In-transit)
Least privilege principle
Security groups, NACLs, firewalls


Category	                    Service

Identity	                     IAM
Encryption	                   KMS
Secrets                     	 Secrets Manager
Logging                     	 CloudTrail
Monitoring	                   CloudWatch
Threat Detection	             GuardDuty
Compliance	                   AWS Config
DDoS                           Protection	Shield
Network                      	 Security Groups, NACLs


Best To Do things-
1)Use MFA everywhere
2)Follow least privilege
3)Encrypt all data
4)Monitor & log EVERYTHING
